.\" Manpage for simple_shell
.TH simple_shell 3 "April 2021" "Version 1.0" "User Commands"

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- interpret and execute lines of commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
[COMMAND] [OPTION]...

.SH DESCRIPTION

simple_shell is a program that read commands and arguments given by the user through the standard input and execute them.

When the simple_shell can't find a command or doesn't recognize an option it will print a message error.

.SH COMMANDS

.IT
.B ls
-list the contents od the directory

.B pwd
- prints the name of the current working directory

.B which
- shows the full path of (shell) commands

.B echo
- shows a line of text

